<para style="q1">

<verse number="3" style="v" />Our God comes and does not stay silent;</para>

<para style="q1">a fire devours before him,</para>

<para style="q1">and it is very stormy around him.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />He calls to the heavens above</para>

<para style="q1">and to the earth so that he may judge his people:</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />"Gather my faithful ones together to me,</para>

<para style="q1">those who have made a covenant with me by sacrifice."</para>
